By":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"一年前入過你個蚊post留言 一年後又係蚊post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔怪得個名咁熟口面"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T18:27:41.000Z","msg":"不忘初衷<br />\n比蚊咬醒一定要殺左先訓<br />\n同佢鬥長命<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZ7tzDP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZ7tzDP.png&h=3f5775dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:10:37.000Z","msg":"蚊乸得個零月命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （如果冇俾人打死）<br />\n認真覆，訓得好地地俾蚊咬醒、之後仲會痕、仲可能會傳播病毒，一下拍死實在便宜咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議樓主買番個電蚊拍，電流唔可以太高，太高一電啲蚊就爆死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要電流低，足以電暈佢一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後捉佢上枱（最好唔好捉佢身，好易整醒，要捉佢啲手手腳腳）再拎啲尖嘢，針又好筆又好，整斷佢對翼（唔好整到佢身，好易整死，整斷半隻翼已經足以令佢飛唔到）正常你咁樣整佢應該會醒，如果唔醒就輕輕篤醒佢（如果死咗就用紙巾包住捽爛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，冇手尾跟）醒咗、又飛唔走你想點玩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係我就會斷佢針之後再斷手腳（確保每個過程隻蚊都係仲有意識）玩到完晒就可以幫佢收屍<br />\n總結：暈&gt;定身&gt;沉默&gt;普攻（啲技唔好升咁高lv就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"7593fd9d06a4f4ff3baf0ab682623a4339579bec","tid":909571,"uid":222623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0399a0fa1fd76f0d7ceb3ff653764d1b64756c","tid":909571,"uid":52683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T23:17:01.000Z","msg":"陷家鈴一晚打咗三隻蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8254156ecc2f757fafc45fa3351d19ed831398","tid":909571,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep